OL,3,CPair who filmed antisemitic abuse of
OL,4,CJewish man for TikTok plead guilty
OL,6,FTwo men who filmed themselves verbally
OL,7,Fabusing a Jewish man in east London
OL,8,Ffor social media have been convicted
OL,9,Fof an antisemitic hate crime, police
OL,10,Fhave said.
OL,12,FAdam Bedoui, 20, and Abdelkader Amir
OL,13,FBousloub, 21, travelled to a
OL,14,Fpredominantly Jewish area of London on
OL,15,FThursday to film antisemitic content
OL,16,Ffor TikTok, the Metropolitan Police
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
