OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778385837
OL,3,CPair who filmed antisemitic abuse of
OL,4,CJewish man for TikTok plead guilty
OL,6,FBoth men pleaded guilty at Thames
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday to a
OL,8,Freligiously aggravated public order
OL,9,Foffence.
OL,11,FThey will be sentenced at the same
OL,12,Fcourt on June 5.
OL,14,F"This was a deliberate and targeted
OL,15,Fantisemitic attack, aggravated by the
OL,16,Fpair's intention to post the incident
OL,17,Fon social media to spread hatred,"
OL,18,FDetective Superintendent Oliver
OL,19,FRichter said on Saturday.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
