OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778385837
OL,3,CPair who filmed antisemitic abuse of
OL,4,CJewish man for TikTok plead guilty
OL,6,F"It is completely unacceptable and has
OL,7,Fno place in London."
OL,9,FPolice were called at around 9pm on
OL,10,FThursday after Bedoui and Bousloub,
OL,11,Fboth of West Drayton in Hillingdon,
OL,12,Fwest London, targeted a Jewish man in
OL,13,FClapton Common, Hackney.
OL,15,FThe two tried to flee when officers
OL,16,Farrived but were swiftly detained, the
OL,17,FMet Police said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
