OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778385837
OL,3,CPair who filmed antisemitic abuse of
OL,4,CJewish man for TikTok plead guilty
OL,6,FTwo 20-year-old men and a 21-year-old
OL,7,Fman were also arrested in connection
OL,8,Fwith the incident and have been
OL,9,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,10,Finquiries, the force also said.
OL,12,F"Our officers acted quickly to arrest
OL,13,Fthose responsible, and within 48 hours
OL,14,Fthey have been brought before the
OL,15,Fcourts and convicted," Mr Richter
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"That should send a clear message: we
OL,19,Fwill act decisively against anyone who
OL,20,Fcommits hate crime.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@VO]zD@AOU
