OL,3,CPair who filmed antisemitic abuse of
OL,4,CJewish man for TikTok plead guilty
OL,6,F"We know the harm incidents like this
OL,7,Fcause to communities and we will
OL,8,Fcontinue to take all reports with the
OL,9,Futmost seriousness."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThis comes after the Metropolitan
OL,17,FPolice announced on Wednesday a
OL,18,Fcommunity protection team of 100 extra
OL,19,Fofficers to help safeguard the Jewish
OL,20,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]
