OL,3,CPair who filmed antisemitic abuse of
OL,4,CJewish man for TikTok plead guilty
OL,6,FIn its initial phase, the new team
OL,7,Fwill be "primarily focused on
OL,8,Fprotecting the Jewish community, which
OL,9,Ffaces some of the highest levels of
OL,10,Fhate crime alongside significant
OL,11,Fterrorist and hostile state threats",
OL,12,Fthe Met Police said.
OL,14,FThey added that it would bring
OL,15,Ftogether "neighbourhood policing,
OL,16,Fspecialist protection and counter
OL,17,Fterrorism capabilities" to provide a
OL,18,F"more visible, intelligenceled and
OL,19,Fcoordinated presence focused on
OL,20,Fprotecting Jewish communities across
OL,21,FLondon".
